<i>noun</i>: 흡착 [흡착], 부합 [부ː합], 고착화 [고차콰] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>흡착 [흡착]</dt><br>
<dd>adhesion</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 물질이 달라붙음.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which a certain substance is attached to something else.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>부합 [부ː합]</dt><br>
<dd>adhesion</dd><br>
<dd>서로 맞대어 붙임.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of joining the surfaces of two parts.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>고착화 [고차콰]</dt><br>
<dd>adhesion</dd><br>
<dd>일정한 상태로 굳어져 변하지 않게 됨. 또는 그렇게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>A state being fixed and not changing, or making this happen.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>